    management: ["Discontinue all nephrotoxic agents immediately", "Maintain euvolemia (avoid both hypovolemia and overhydration)", "Monitor and correct electrolyte imbalances aggressively", "Renal replacement therapy if indicated (refractory hyperkalemia, severe acidosis, uremic symptoms, fluid overload)", "Adjust all medication doses for reduced GFR", "Nutritional support with appropriate protein restriction"],
